Project Title: Responsive Landing Page (Next.js + Tailwind + Vercel v0)
Objective

Build a fully responsive, modern, clean landing page for a product/service/website using:

Next.js (App Router)

Tailwind CSS

Vercel v0 (mandatory for UI generation)

Deployed on Vercel

